        "value": "{\\displaystyle {\\begin{aligned}\\operatorname {E} \\left[X^{2}\\right]&=\\int _{0}^{\\infty }x^{2}\\lambda e^{-\\lambda x}\\,dx\\\\&={\\left[-x^{2}e^{-\\lambda x}\\right]}_{0}^{\\infty }+\\int _{0}^{\\infty }2xe^{-\\lambda x}\\,dx\\\\&=0+{\\frac {2}{\\lambda }}\\operatorname {E} [X]\\\\&={\\frac {2}{\\lambda ^{2}}}.\\end{aligned}}}"
