        "value": "{\\displaystyle {\\begin{aligned}\\operatorname {Var} (X)&=\\sum _{i=1}^{6}{\\frac {1}{6}}\\left(i-{\\frac {7}{2}}\\right)^{2}\\\\[5pt]&={\\frac {1}{6}}\\left((-5/2)^{2}+(-3/2)^{2}+(-1/2)^{2}+(1/2)^{2}+(3/2)^{2}+(5/2)^{2}\\right)\\\\[5pt]&={\\frac {35}{12}}\\approx 2.92.\\end{aligned}}}"
