        "value": "{\\displaystyle {\\begin{aligned}\\operatorname {Var} (X)&=\\operatorname {E} \\left(X^{2}\\right)-(\\operatorname {E} (X))^{2}\\\\[5pt]&={\\frac {1}{n}}\\sum _{i=1}^{n}i^{2}-\\left({\\frac {1}{n}}\\sum _{i=1}^{n}i\\right)^{2}\\\\[5pt]&={\\frac {(n+1)(2n+1)}{6}}-\\left({\\frac {n+1}{2}}\\right)^{2}\\\\[4pt]&={\\frac {n^{2}-1}{12}}.\\end{aligned}}}"
