        "value": "{\\displaystyle {\\begin{aligned}\\operatorname {Var} (X+Y)&=\\operatorname {E} \\left[(X+Y)^{2}\\right]-(\\operatorname {E} [X+Y])^{2}\\\\[5pt]&=\\operatorname {E} \\left[X^{2}+2XY+Y^{2}\\right]-(\\operatorname {E} [X]+\\operatorname {E} [Y])^{2}.\\end{aligned}}}"
